  ('dietitian-moex-10446', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某縣市進行一項麵粉營養素富化（enrichment）計畫，計畫之目的在改善該縣市社區居民維生素B 營養狀況 2 ；該縣衛生局於計畫結束時，以隨機抽樣方法抽取居民，並分析其血液中維生素B 的濃度作為計畫成果評 2 量之依據。請問此種評量屬於： 過程評量（process evaluation）  全方位評量（goal-free evaluation） 效果評量（effectiveness evaluation）  效益評量（cost-effective evaluation）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1ecb2ba898bd", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10447', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '為提高民眾對營養標示的認知與應用，某基金會於便利超商提供相關宣導單張，請問此便利超商即是行銷 策略常用之4P中所謂的： promotion  place  price  plan', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1ecb2ba898bd", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10448', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '社區營養計畫執行過程中需要不同的管理階層，請問下列各種管理技巧所占比率，何者適合低階的管理階層？ 技術＞人際關係＞概念    概念＞人際關係＞技術 人際關係＞技術＞概念    概念＞技術＞人際關係', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1ecb2ba898bd", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10449', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某營養師在策畫一項營養改善計畫時，將改善對象依年齡層及性別加以區分後，再依各族群特性分別訂定 計畫內容。請問此種規畫方式稱為： 分層規畫  特殊化  特質化  市場區隔', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "1ecb2ba898bd", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
